---
description: LOCK PROJECT STRUCTURE
globs: ["**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

This app already has an established structure.

Strictly forbidden unless explicitly requested:
- do not rename files
- do not rename folders
- do not move files
- do not invent a new architecture
- do not split files into many new files unless requested
- do not merge unrelated files
- do not change folder conventions
- do not change aliases or path conventions unless required for a real fix
- do not delete files unless explicitly requested

Preferred behavior:
- make the smallest possible diff
- edit existing files in place
- preserve existing file names
- preserve current folder layout
- keep imports stable where possible

Default behavior:
preserve project structure exactly.
